data.Name: Beyond North
data.Bio: Beyond North - band from Germany (Bonn, North Rhine-Westphalia). Formed in 1994. Last known line-up Michael Pelkowsky. Discography - Demo 1994, The Dark Is My Father - 1995 , Spectaculum - 2000 and unofficial edition North awaits - Demo Tape 1993 Deliver us from God - Tape 1995 Hymns of Darkness - Tape 1995 Read more on Last.fm
